    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/3db2a11558a7f0601d3998e8b2c8385e.avif?t=1754569075\" width=610 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《梦之形：序章》是一款将MOBA战斗与动作Rogue-like元素融合的游戏，《梦之形》的免费序章版本。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >梦与现实之间的中间世界，急流</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/78655ddcec4189d1aada1bbd0c516186.avif?t=1754569075\" width=610 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某一天，梦境与现实的界限崩溃，通过维度裂隙，人们可以往来于名为“急流”的中间世界。随着一个源自未知的传言，声称到达梦境的尽头可以实现任何愿望，英雄们各自带着自己的理由踏入这个未知的世界。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >记忆编辑</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/09f82259acda2d47bc34496e4a6937d3.poster.avif?t=1754569075\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/09f82259acda2d47bc34496e4a6937d3.webm?t=1754569075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/09f82259acda2d47bc34496e4a6937d3.mp4?t=1754569075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以编辑自己的记忆，创造独一无二的角色。利用过去的记忆在战斗中击败敌人。将神秘的宝石、精华附加到记忆上，赋予特殊效果并创造协同作用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >近战攻击异常强大的远程输出？自爆法师？一切皆有可能！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >揭开急流的秘密</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/da08360ad125bb1999ebe51f116e9dd3.avif?t=1754569075\" width=610 height=276 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梦境世界总是在变化。在这个程序生成的世界中，梦境居民、任务、各种事件和隐藏的秘密等待着您的探索。世界中存在的各种秘密将在每一局中提供新的体验。在这个过程中，解锁超过200种收集元素。但要小心，猎手们总是在监视您。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >无尽的挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/a11f0869516bd8e9ce91a2ab6bab680b.poster.avif?t=1754569075\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/a11f0869516bd8e9ce91a2ab6bab680b.webm?t=1754569075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/a11f0869516bd8e9ce91a2ab6bab680b.mp4?t=1754569075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于有难度选择和永久升级系统，即使您的游戏技能不是很高，也能享受《梦之形》的全部内容。如果您喜欢挑战，急流的规则可以通过清醒梦直接改变，还有强大的隐藏首领等残酷的试炼等待着您。克服这些试炼，证明自己的实力！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的角色和玩法风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275270/extras/916a2705639ebc10509aba2bf29f6d63.avif?t=1754569075\" width=610 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您对极限控制有信心吗？那么推荐快速敏捷的近战角色薄雾！坚固强大的坦克角色维斯珀怎么样？或者您想作为远程输出带领朋友们取得胜利吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《梦之形》准备了远程输出、打击者、坦克、法师等多种角色类型。找到适合您的玩法风格的角色。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独自或与朋友一起</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《梦之形》虽然提供了完整的单人游戏体验，但也支持最多4人的合作多人游戏。通过丰富的互动系统，如治疗、增益和群体控制，体验卓越的协作体验！</p>",
